title: âš¡Washington Freedom Beats San Francisco Unicorns by 30 Runs in MLC
body: The Washington Freedom moved to the second spot on the points table after defeating San Francisco Unicorns by 30 runs in Major League Cricket at Church Street Park, Morrisville on Saturday. Meanwhile, the Unicorns remained in fourth place with two wins from four matches. The Washington Freedom posted a total of 133/8 in their 20 overs before bowling out the Unicorns for 103.
summary:
* Result: Washington Freedom defeated San Francisco Unicorns by 30 runs
* Current standing: Washington Freedom moved to second spot on the points table, while San Francisco Unicorns remained in fourth place with two wins from four matches
* Match details: Washington Freedom scored 133/8 in 20 overs, and then bowled out San Francisco Unicorns for 103
